Advanced Administration Set (admin)

The Advanced Administration Set provides packages that allow more
experienced users to perform more advanced administration tasks via
a menu-driven user interface and expands the backup and restore
capabilities of the basic system.  This set includes the following
packages:

OPERATIONS ADMINISTRATION AND MAINTENANCE (oam)

The Operations Administration and Maintenance Package provides a
character-based, menu-oriented interface to a wide variety of advanced,
server-oriented tasks for use by an experienced system administrator.
The Advanced Commands Package must be installed before installing this
package.

FACE (face)

The FACE Package provides a user-friendly, character-based interface
to the system based on an "office" metaphor. The Advanced Commands Package
must be installed before installing this package.

EXTENDED BACKUP AND RESTORE (bkrs)

The Extended Backup and Restore Package includes a flexible set of backup and
restore utilities useful on machines with lots of disk space.  The
Operations Administration and Maintenance Package must be installed before
installing this package.
